The paper discusses relevance feedback techniques for information retrieval, specifically for retrieving answer passages. This topic falls under the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of semantic matching and natural language processing techniques, which are relevant to sub-categories such as Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the limitations and potential of new environments such as voice-based search with smart home devices, which could be relevant to the sub-category of Cybernetics (cs.CY).
